    <td align="left" valign="top"><font face="Verdana" size="2">
    Obtained from Camlen in the Temple of Lifein Qeynos. You must return the No Drop Lore Pestilence Scythe dropped by the Live/Human version of Lord Grimrot and the Decaying Heart of Lord Grimrot dropped by the skeleton version, both spawn in South Karana.<br><br>
Can also be wore on the back.</font>
